在印度斯坦語中實義詞(content word)通常開始於低[[音調|音調]]，隨後音調升高。<ref>http://www.und.nodak.edu/dept/linguistics/theses/2001Dyrud.PDF {{Wayback|url=http://www.und.nodak.edu/dept/linguistics/theses/2001Dyrud.PDF |date=20120207033117 }} Dyrud, Lars O. (2001)  ''Hindi-Urdu: Stress Accent or Non-Stress Accent?'' (University of North Dakota, master's thesis)</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.speech.sri.com/people/rao/papers/icslp96_wbhyp.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-10-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071025082631/http://www.speech.sri.com/people/rao/papers/icslp96_wbhyp.pdf |archivedate=2007-10-25 }} Ramana Rao, G.V. and Srichand, J. (1996)  ''Word Boundary Detection Using Pitch Variations.'' ([[IIT_Madras|IIT Madras]], Dept. of Computer Science and Engineering)</ref> 嚴格的說，印地語-烏爾都語像多數其他印度語言一樣，更像是[[音節等時|音節等時]]語言。[[schwa|schwa]] {{IPA|/ə/}} 有著在非重音音節中省略的強烈趨勢。

